[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA Jazzer‐based fuzzing run triggered a [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical exception indicating a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile path traversal issue during archive expansion in the Apache Commons Compress [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Expander` example code. The sanitizer detected an attempt to write files outside [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe intended output directory.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Issue  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The fuzzer input caused the archive expander to process an entry whose file path [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolved outside the designated extraction directory. The built‐in [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FilePathTraversal` sanitizer raised a critical security exception when it detected[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe unsafe path.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Vulnerability Type  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  File path traversal – archive entries containing sequences [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., “..”[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lead to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction of files to unintended locations.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key Observations  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The exception originates from [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.FilePathTraversal.check[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The offending path check happens in `[0m[1;35mFilePathTraversal.copyMismatchMvHook[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The call stack shows multiple overloads of [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35morg.apache.commons.compress.archivers.examples.Expander.expand[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` before reaching [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe sanitizer  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ExpanderFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m merely feeds inputs to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Expander.expand`; it is not the root cause[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Components to Investigate  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `org.apache.commons.compress.archivers.examples.Expander` class, especially:  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m methods and overloads  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – `[0m[1;35mcopyMismatchMvHook[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and any internal path normalization logic  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `com.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.FilePathTraversal` for its path [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation logic  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. The interaction between archive entry names and target file path construction [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand where traversal checks are enforced.[0m                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35morg.apache.commons.compress.archivers.examples.Expander.expand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExpander.jav[0m[1;92ma:502[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This indicates the code did not properly guard against archive entries with [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtraversal paths [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `..[0m[35m/[0m[95moutside[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Important Observations  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sanitizer raised the issue before any real I/O corruption, as part of a [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msecurity check.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The stack trace pins the behavior to `FilePathTraversal.copyMismatchMvHook` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand then into the `Expander.expand` logic.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ExpanderFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m drives [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Expander.expand`, but the root cause lies inside `Expander.expand`.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch removes `import java.nio.channels.Channels;` and switches to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Files.newOutputStream` for writing entries.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inside `expand`, it introduces:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Resolution of each `[0m[1;35mentry.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` against the absolute, normalized [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`targetDirectory` path.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • A check to ensure `[0m[1;35mdestPath.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`; on failure, an [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` is thrown.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Directory creation for directory entries and parent directories for files.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • File writing via `try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOutputStream out = [0m[1;35mFiles.newOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdestPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mIOUtils.copyLarge[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Invocation of the consumer callback `[0m[1;35mc.accept[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdestFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` after each entry.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Patch Result and Build Log  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEDUP_TOKEN: 7bb3f9683ba8f59b[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a Jazzer-detected `FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical` exception [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating a file path traversal vulnerability in the `Expander` example class when[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextracting archive entries. The user submitted a patch that introduces a new [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream‐based `expand` method with explicit path normalization and directory [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcreation using `Files.createDirectories`, removes the old `createParentDirectory` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhelper, and adjusts the main dispatch in `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat, closeableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. After[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying the patch, the project fails to compile with errors about a duplicate [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`expand` method, missing symbols [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`createParentDirectory` and [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CloseableConsumerAdapter.accept`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and unresolved references in `Expander.java`.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Jazzer reports a critical security issue:  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical: File path [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtraversal: [0m[35m/tmp/.../[0m[95mjazzer-traversal[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      at [0m[1;35mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.FilePathTraversal.check[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      at [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35morg.apache.commons.compress.archivers.examples.Expander.expand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExpander.jav[0m[1;92ma:502[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[33m...[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      at [0m[1;35mExpanderFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExpanderFuzzer.jav[0m[1;92ma:52[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The exception arises during archive expansion in `Expander.expand`, indicating [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat some extracted entry name resolved outside the target directory.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key observations:  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The existing `Expander` uses a custom `createParentDirectory` helper to walk [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand create directories, handling symlinks manually.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The path-traversal sanitizer is triggered before or during file creation under [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma temporary directory.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In the main `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString format, CloseableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, the patch adds an [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearly return branch that delegates non-seekable archives to a newly introduced [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstream-based overload:  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```diff[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  -    [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat, [0m[1;35mc.track[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mChannels.newInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39marchive[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, targetDirectory, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCloseableConsumer.NULL_CONSUMER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  +    try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream is = [0m[1;35mChannels.newInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39marchive[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  +        [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat, is, targetDirectory, closeableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  +    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  +    return;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adds a new `public void [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString format, InputStream archiveStream, Path [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtargetDirectory, CloseableConsumer closeableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` overload that:  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Wraps `ArchiveInputStream` creation via `ArchiveStreamFactory`.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Computes a normalized absolute `base` path.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Normalizes `dest = [0m[1;35mbase.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mentry.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and throws [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` if `![0m[1;35mdest.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbase[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Calls `Files.createDirectories` for parents or entry directories and copies [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Invokes `[0m[1;35mc.accept[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mdest.toFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on the `CloseableConsumerAdapter`.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removes the old `createParentDirectory` helper and related code comments.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch-Result Logs  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maven compilation errors in `Expander.java`:  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Duplicate method definition:  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     method [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString, InputStream, Path, CloseableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is already defined[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min class Expander[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Missing symbol `[0m[1;35maccept[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on `CloseableConsumerAdapter`:  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cannot find symbol: method [0m[1;35maccept[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m location: variable c of type [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCloseableConsumerAdapter[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. References to the removed helper `createParentDirectory` remain in other [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods:  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     cannot find symbol: method [0m[1;35mcreateParentDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPath, Path[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- As a result, the build fails immediately with four compilation errors.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `Expander` example class:  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Locate and reconcile existing `expand` method overloads to avoid duplicates.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Update or restore references to `createParentDirectory` or remove all its call [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msites.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `CloseableConsumerAdapter` API:  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Verify whether it exposes an `[0m[1;35maccept[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method or requires a different [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcallback method.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The main `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat, channel, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` dispatch logic:  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Ensure the new branch integrates without conflicting with ZIP/TAR/SEVEN_Z [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdispatch cases.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any other examples or utility classes that invoke `createParentDirectory` or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverload `expand`.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis evaluation summarizes the security report, the attempted remediation, and the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation failures, and identifies the precise locations in `Expander.java` and [0m  [2m                [0m
